{"tid":973454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學副校長被爆偷食女學生致其懷孕流產 省紀委介入","createTime":"2019-01-08T07:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T09:43:36.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45e054b0cb32611238e18c13c797c27e1eeba51c","tid":973454,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%87%B4%E5%85%B6%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E6%B5%81%E7%94%A2-%E7%9C%81%E7%B4%80%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%8B-230455254.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2581%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%25B6%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E6%25B5%2581%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E7%259C%2581%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%258B-230455254.html&d=2R0LF9gRtTAaEL5r1VG0OP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=696c0314\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%89%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E5%81%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%87%B4%E5%85%B6%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E6%B5%81%E7%94%A2-%E7%9C%81%E7%B4%80%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%8B-230455254.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇淮安市的淮陰師範學院一名女畢業生，向校方致函舉報，副校長李x銀與她有長達兩年的婚外情，並致其懷孕和流產。李男家人多次對其騷擾辱罵，致她患上重度抑鬱症。校方已將舉報材料轉交給江蘇省紀委，省紀委已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n涉事女生王雪（化名）是該校文學院2014級的學生。她透露於2016年9月，她剛上大三時，李男就報銷和整理發票一事要求王雪上他的家。她說︰「他就在我面前說他很喜歡我啊，喜歡我很久，然後他就過來抱我，他就要脫我衣服嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n王雪去年11月向該校紀律檢查委員會遞交舉報信，稱李男「拒絕道歉，毫無悔改之意」，還指示其家人對她言語上的侮辱、威脅與恐嚇，使她的生活造成嚴重的困擾，屬於違法行為。王雪呈交的舉報材料中還有李男發給她的多張裸照，以及騷擾短訊、生日卡和情詩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n副校長真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78b807b4aaf4df75420c0fc013217a7d10cd286","tid":973454,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"省紀委執雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e061f1530ee17c736a1c070da95031e7978950f","tid":973454,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20幾碎 一定好正"},{"pid":"ed3f4f7f4afdbe9361ae9fbf05cf40a38ab58e5e","tid":973454,"uid":11301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e061f1530ee17c736a1c070da95031e7978950f","tid":973454,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20幾碎 一定好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"碎你老母"},{"pid":"4d28f547448cd748c2f1748d0826428eda101082","tid":973454,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ed3f4f7f4afdbe9361ae9fbf05cf40a38ab58e5e","tid":973454,"uid":11301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e061f1530ee17c736a1c070da95031e7978950f","tid":973454,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20幾碎 一定好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"碎你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\